{
  "openapi": "3.0.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "RPC - Platform Operations",
    "description": "Cisco IOS-XE RPC Operations - Platform\n\n**Category:** Platform Operations\n**Modules:** 2\n**RPC Actions:** 2\n\n**HTTP Methods:**\n- POST: Execute RPC action/operation\n\n**Modules Included:**\n- power-supply\n- stack-power\n\n**RPC Operation Pattern:**\nRPC operations are executed via RESTCONF POST to `/operations/` endpoints.\nEach RPC accepts input parameters and returns output results.\n\n**Example RPC Execution:**\n```bash\nPOST /restconf/operations/Cisco-IOS-XE-rpc:ping\nContent-Type: application/yang-data+json\n\n{\n  \"input\": {\n    \"ping-request\": {\n      \"destination\": \"10.0.0.1\",\n      \"repeat-count\": 5,\n      \"size\": 100\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Example Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"output\": {\n    \"ping-reply\": {\n      \"destination\": \"10.0.0.1\",\n      \"request-count\": 5,\n      \"reply-count\": 5,\n      \"success-rate\": 100,\n      \"minimum-rtt\": 1,\n      \"average-rtt\": 2,\n      \"maximum-rtt\": 3\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Common Operations:**\n- power_supply_rpc:set-pwr-supply-slot-state\n- stack_power_rpc:set-stkpwr-port-state\n\n",
    "version": "17.18.1"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "https://{device}/restconf",
      "variables": {
        "device": {
          "default": "router.example.com",
          "description": "Device IP or hostname"
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/operations/power_supply_rpc:set-pwr-supply-slot-state": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "Set the stack slot status for a switch.",
        "description": "**Source Module:** power-supply\n\nSet the stack slot status for a switch.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /restconf/operations/power_supply_rpc:set-pwr-supply-slot-state`",
        "operationId": "set-pwr-supply-slot-state",
        "tags": [
          "Cisco-IOS-XE-power-supply-rpc"
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/yang-data+json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "power_supply_rpc:set-pwr-supply-slot-state": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                      "switch-number": {
                        "type": "integer",
                        "minimum": 1,
                        "maximum": 16,
                        "description": "Switch number"
                      },
                      "slot": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Power supply slot name"
                      },
                      "state": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Power supply slot state"
                      },
                      "supply": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "properties": {
                          "switch-number": {
                            "type": "integer",
                            "minimum": 1,
                            "maximum": 16,
                            "description": "Switch number"
                          },
                          "slot": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "Power supply slot name"
                          },
                          "state": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "Power supply slot state"
                          }
                        },
                        "required": [
                          "switch-number",
                          "slot",
                          "state"
                        ],
                        "description": "Set the power supply slot & state"
                      }
                    },
                    "required": [
                      "switch-number",
                      "slot",
                      "state"
                    ]
                  }
                }
              },
              "example": {
                "power_supply_rpc:set-pwr-supply-slot-state": {
                  "switch-number": 10,
                  "slot": "example-string",
                  "state": "example-string",
                  "supply": {
                    "switch-number": 10,
                    "slot": "example-string",
                    "state": "example-string"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "RPC executed successfully",
            "content": {
              "application/yang-data+json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object"
                },
                "example": {}
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "Invalid input"
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "Unauthorized"
          },
          "500": {
            "description": "Internal server error"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/operations/stack_power_rpc:set-stkpwr-port-state": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "Set the stack port status for a switch.",
        "description": "**Source Module:** stack-power\n\nSet the stack port status for a switch.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /restconf/operations/stack_power_rpc:set-stkpwr-port-state`",
        "operationId": "set-stkpwr-port-state",
        "tags": [
          "Cisco-IOS-XE-stack-power-rpc"
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/yang-data+json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "stack_power_rpc:set-stkpwr-port-state": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                      "switch-number": {
                        "type": "integer",
                        "minimum": 1,
                        "maximum": 16,
                        "description": "Switch number"
                      },
                      "port-number": {
                        "type": "integer",
                        "minimum": 1,
                        "maximum": 2,
                        "description": "Stack port number"
                      },
                      "stkpwr-state": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Stack port state"
                      }
                    },
                    "required": [
                      "switch-number",
                      "port-number",
                      "stkpwr-state"
                    ]
                  }
                }
              },
              "example": {
                "stack_power_rpc:set-stkpwr-port-state": {
                  "switch-number": 10,
                  "port-number": 8080,
                  "stkpwr-state": "example-string"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "RPC executed successfully",
            "content": {
              "application/yang-data+json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object"
                },
                "example": {}
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "Invalid input"
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "Unauthorized"
          },
          "500": {
            "description": "Internal server error"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
